Name:           perl-Color-Library
Version:        0.021
Release:        alt2_3
Summary:        Easy-to-use and comprehensive named-color library
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Perl
URL:            http://search.cpan.org/dist/Color-Library/
